message.body: Hey, do you want to come get tools today? I gotta drive the van for emissions again and get a toilet and do a bunch of other crap so I want to plan my day.
I'm out for a while. I could get my stuff this evening or tomorrow
Tonight would be better preferably before it gets dark but I'll be around after 5 tomorrow.
I could come by in twenty minutes
Watching a movie at Liz's. Can it be at 7? If not we can do tomorrow.
Ok. I'll text when it's over.
Hey , I'm done. Meet at my place in 15?
Ok. I got class at night

Ok. I'm not in a rush and the electrical stuff is at a job that's getting finished on Wednesday so maybe we can just meet after that. I've put some of your stuff aside already but I can collect the rest and have it for you later in the week if that makes more sense.
